section.def:
relevant CIS property (相關集體投資計劃財產) has
           the meaning given by Part 2 of Schedule 5 to the Ordinance;
               (L.N. 58 of 2023)

subparagraph.content:
where it is licensed for Type 13 regulated activity, an analysis of
                        relevant CIS property received or held by it for any relevant CIS arising
                        from the carrying on of Type 13 regulated activity; and (L.N. 58 of 2023)
